{"tid":1473192,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際文宣標題] 歷史不斷重演 下一次六四事情=香港","createTime":"2019-08-14T18:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T02:50:58.000Z","uid":229033,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bb2792c7999ebeb6cdb3a8583a43493afd4f5711","tid":1473192,"uid":229033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:51:22.000Z","msg":"有個提議<br />\n<br />\n國際文宣標題/大方向<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">歷史不斷重演 - 下一次六四事件=香港<br />\n</span></strong></strong></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">英文唔好9up brainstorm 屌細力啲</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>History repeats itself<br />\nThe NEXT 1989 tinanmen square crackdown =HONG KONG</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n相信全世界除左中國之外<br />\n無人夠膽講<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">六四事件係最低武力</span></span></ins><br />\n無人夠膽講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">六四事件係偶然發生</span></ins></span><br />\n無人夠膽講<ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">六四事件係無證據嘅指控</span></span></ins><br />\n<br />\n每個外國人都一定聽過 睇過 了解過六四當年鎮壓<br />\n係有幾咁慘絕人寰 幾咁恐怖<br />\n<br />\n所以為左確保中共唔會真係比我地批中上演六四翻版<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地必須先發制人 我地一樣要話比全世界知<br />\n我地已經開始左六四翻版事件<br />\n只有咁樣，其他國家嘅外交部先會出手</span><br />\n<br />\n而且散左風出去，可能會吸引到更多嘅外國記者黎<br />\n萬一真係發生咩事，至少多個紀錄都好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><strong>記得配圖可以多啲用被迫害嘅相 配合一個中性設計<br />\n切忌同法輪功走同一路線<br />\n</strong></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b73609ac7fea837df248a0518f5cfc6ebdf4b089","tid":1473192,"uid":229033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:51:47.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"691c81d8ce945be186117f67b479b1d292a3c80f","tid":1473192,"uid":229033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:51:58.000Z","msg":"十"},